title: Candice Thompson
itunes:title: Candice Thompson
description:
Comedian, writer, actor Candice Thompson (THE TONIGHT SHOW, LATE SHOW WITH STEPHEN COLBERT, LIGHTS OUT WITH DAVID SPADE) is our guest this week and she and Whitney get into everything from conspiracy theories to tripping on poisonous secretions of giant monkey frogs (KAMBO) to urine therapy.  Check out Candice's podcast NOSY NEIGHBORS wherever you get your podcasts.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
